{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2893849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是现在的经济学在加深贫困", "timestamp": 1636426565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893850, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然但是，是什么给你的错觉，认为经管很多人在通过经济学解决贫困", "timestamp": 1636426565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893853, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而不是在制造贫困", "timestamp": 1636426572, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893867, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "呼吁：解决贫困问题靠马克思的经济学！", "timestamp": 1636426657, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893921, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2893853, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 经济学是加深贫困，制造贫困，那就没有人在解决贫困了。", "timestamp": 1636426907, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893937, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2893921, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哦？那你觉得现在学的经济学怎么解决贫困", "timestamp": 1636426996, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893946, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2893921, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 经济在accumulate，但是又不归穷人所有", "timestamp": 1636427028, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893948, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2893937, "tag": null, "text": "很想引用🐴☁被喷的那句话：商业是最大的慈善", "timestamp": 1636427043, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2893973, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2893948, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这不就是资本家的观点吗", "timestamp": 1636427242, "typ