要矛盾哪些是次要的现在应该还是挺明显的吧", "timestamp": 1636427975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894075, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894062, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 所以Alice的论点是经济学不是解决贫困的学科，马院的研究才是？", "timestamp": 1636428122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894085, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894075, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz的观点是这些都是研究解决贫困的学科，都属于经济学。", "timestamp": 1636428278, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894091, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894085, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哪个有用用哪个。有用的衡量标准是数据。", "timestamp": 1636428334, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894091, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那数据拿出来吧", "timestamp": 1636428431, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894113, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且dz引的原洞代指的经济学恐怕不同于dz的经济学", "timestamp": 1636428481, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894122, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也好希望经济学能解决这些问题啊！但谁去解决啊！那么多掌握经济学武器的人们，偏偏利用经济学继续加深贫困，这有什么办法", "timestamp": 1636428608, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894122, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 加大贫困差距不等于加深贫困。", "timestamp": 1636428685, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894122, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: “武器”……", "timestamp": 1636428752, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894146, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894122, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 实证的经济学是一门科学，是为了总结现象背后的规律，就像物理学家掌握了物理规律的“武器”，但总不能指望物理学家都去搬砖打靶吧", "timestamp": 1636428875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894128, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz认为欧洲工人的翻身是公会斗争的力量还是经济学的自发力量", "timestamp": 1636428880, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894146, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 可以指望物理学家造核武器，也可以指望经济学家进一步给予剥削的方法", "timestamp": 1636428968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894160, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894153, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 当然也可以指望经济学家做相反的事情 but他们不做", "timestamp": 1636429061, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894153, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我感觉Alice的想象和我看到的经济学研究相当不同", "timestamp": 1636429199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894176, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894172, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 你可以讲一讲来纠正我的看法", "timestamp": 1636429231, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894179, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894160, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 政策制定者参考经济学家的建议和研究成果，经济学家研究政策，但并不意味着经济学家就是政策制定者", "timestamp": 1636429246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894184, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894176, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 也不是纠正吧…只是我看到的大部分研究者没有这方面的追求，或者说，这不是当前学术研究的重点和主流", "timestamp": 1636429295, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894184, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是的，像Alice想回答的🐴的经济学好还是其他经济学好的问题，也是经济学的研究范围呀", "timestamp": 1636429891, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894541, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894274, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 至于这个问题的答案是什么，与本洞的论点无关。Alice如果想讨论，可以开一个zzxg的洞，dz进去讨论学习。", "timestamp": 1636431620, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894781, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "alice的话看了令人不禁感叹一句无知的力量最强大", "timestamp": 1636433506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2894835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现有经济 金融的教育或工作或研究，真的是在减少贫困吗", "timestamp": 1636433792, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2895287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894835, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 很大一部分都是吧。虽然没有减小贫富差距，但穷人的生活也越来越好了。", "timestamp": 1636437221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2895299, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2895287, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 制定经济政策的时候要参考各方面的经济学工作/研究都为经济健康发展做出了贡献", "timestamp": 1636437348, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2898061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "穷人的生活变好主要是因为生产力提高了吧，政策上的倾斜也是，不然自由市场的经济学怎么可能去解决偏远山区的贫困问题呢？", "timestamp": 1636461086, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2899530, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2894541, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 笑嘻了，经管出来的做量化去投行去咨询是解决贫困是吧😅", "timestamp": 1636473232, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2903309, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2899530, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 是的，即使在纯自由市场美国，穷人的生活也是越来越好的。量化投行也为经济平稳发展做出了贡献。", "timestamp": 1636517661, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2903357, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2899530, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 这是解决贫困最快的方式。", "timestamp": 1636518024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2903380, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2903357, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 在自由市场的经济学中，只要贫困山区的人出来打工，参与外界经济活动，他们的生活就正在被改善，只不过改善的比较慢罢了。如果没有被改善，他们不会bother出来打工的。", "timestamp": 1636518238, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2903469, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2903357, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这是很多经济学家的观点，验证他们是否成立也要靠经管老师同学从业者的工作/科研。这个观点目前和dz的观测是相符的，所以dz相信这个观点。", "timestamp": 1636518796, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2912420, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 550560, "reply_to": 2903309, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1636625849, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 550560, "reply": 47, "tag": null, "text": "#550128\n解决贫困靠的正是经济学，而不是宗教式的自我感动和道德绑架", "timestamp": 1636425797, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636625847, "url": "", "vote": {}}}